    • Method Detail

      • execute

        Tuple<java.util.Collection<ExecutionLineageNode>,​java.util.Collection<ChannelInstance>> execute​(ChannelInstance[] inputs,
                                                                                                      ChannelInstance[] outputs,
                                                                                                      GiraphExecutor giraphExecutor,
                                                                                                      OptimizationContext.OperatorContext operatorContext)
        Evaluates this operator. Takes a set of inputs and produces a set of outputs.

        In addition, this method should give feedback of what this instance was doing by wiring the LazyExecutionLineageNodes of input and ouput ChannelInstances and providing a Collection of executed OptimizationContext.OperatorContexts.

        Parameters:
        inputs - ChannelInstances that satisfy the inputs of this operator
        outputs - ChannelInstances that collect the outputs of this operator
        operatorContext - OptimizationContext.OperatorContext of this instance
        Returns:
        Collections of what has been executed and produced
